privateJob.title: Flipkart Off Campus Recruitment 2021-Apply Online for various vacancies in Karnataka
privateJob.body:
Name of the post:

  • Software Development Engineer

Description:

Flipkart has issued a notification to fill the vacancies of various posts of Software Development Engineer.If you are finding jobs in Karnataka then feel free to apply online from The ProGrad .The candidates who are interested in the vacancies issued by Flipkart can see the detailed information about key skills required, educational qualification, total vacancies, how to apply, roles, and responsibilities are given below. Flipkart is dealing with online Shopping. If you are interested then read the details that are given below.

Total vacancies:

  • Various vacancies have released.

Selection Process:

  • Personal Interview

Role and responsibility:

  • As a Software Development Engineer, you will contribute to all the aspects of the solve - data and application engineering, data sciences.
  • Implement systems with good low-level design, having the right separation of concerns, uses correct data structures, enabling ease of experimentation
  • Troubleshoot most issues in owned component(s) by himself/herself
  • Design & implement efficient data pipelines (data modeling/schema, data transformation, aggregations, robustness, etc) for the scope of the problem.
  • Take non-functional requirement (Reliability & Availability, Scale, horizontal scalability) into considerations while taking any decision
  • Build, develop, mentor and coach junior team members
  • Collaborate with teams by contributing to the shared vision and working closely with cross-functional stakeholders.

Application fee:

  • No information is given about the application required.

Educational qualification:

The candidates who are interested to apply for Flipkart jobs, you must have the following qualification:

  • The candidates must have completed the BTECH/MTECH from a recognized university to apply for the application Flipkart Off-Campus Recruitment 2021

Key skills required :

The candidates who are interested to apply in these job openings must have the following key skills that are required to do this:

  • Deep expertise in at least one programming language & tech stack.
  • Strong object-oriented design skills, ability to apply design patterns, and an uncanny ability to design intuitive module and class-level interfaces
  • Experience in building data-driven web application design and development is a plus
  • Good understanding of multiple tech solutions and ability to pick the correct one for the given situation
  • Prior work experience in an agile environment or continuous integration and continuous delivery (CI or CD)
  • Ability and experience in designing high-level software designs of the scalable system, taking NFR (non-functional requirement) in consideration

Payscale info. :

  • The Payscale information will be decided at the time of the interview.

The document needs to be carried:

The candidates who will be selected for the interview must carry the below-mentioned documents:

  • The first and foremost thing is your resume/CV which has your educational background and other related information.
  • You must have your Adhaar card for identity purposes.
  • You must have other identity proofs like a PAN card, voter id, or Passport to prove your citizenship.
  • At last, you should have photocopies of important educational certificates.

How to apply for Flipkart Off-Campus Recruitment 2021?

Candidates who are eligible and interested to apply for Flipkart Job then you should follow the below steps to apply:

Note: You can also apply by clicking the apply now button shown above to apply directly from here

  • First of all, read the Flipkart Off Campus Recruitment 2021 notification thoroughly at the official website link.
  • You should have an email id and a phone number for communication purposes.
  • Click on the apply now link for the post you want to apply for.
  • Fill in the required details and submit.
  • Pay the application fee asked for.
  • Finally submit and download the application form for future purposes.
